Package: NAATools
Type: Package
Title: NA-Accord Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Erik Westlund
Maintainer: Erik Westlund <ewestlund@jhu.edu>
Description: This package provides tools to pull down, clean, and analyze data 
  from the NA-Accord Depot. Includes support for data standardization through 
  canonical value lookup tables, file summarization, synthetic data generation,
  and metadata-driven file characterization.
License: Proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
